      <title>拜登在追悼会上承诺支持新奥尔良</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/biden-pledges-support-to-new-orleans-during-memorial-service</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登在与元旦新奥尔良袭击受害者家属举行的祈祷仪式上表示哀悼，并承诺提供联邦政府的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/biden-pledges-support-to-new-orleans-during-memorial-service</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 01:57:26 GMT</pubDate>
